{"id":241,"parent_id":238,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":241,"title":"James 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"James","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","By governing the tongue, we gain perfection—Heavenly wisdom is pure, peaceable, and full of mercy."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.1","order":"03.22.003.24999"},["b","1"],"My brethren,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"be"],"not many",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"masters"],", knowing that we shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"receive"],"the greater condemnation."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.2","order":"03.22.003.25000"},["b","2"],"For in many things we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"offend all"],". If any man",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"offend not"],"in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"word"],", the same",["i","is"],"a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"perfect"],"man,",["i","and"],"able also to bridle the whole body."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.3","order":"03.22.003.25001"},["b","3"],"Behold, we put bits in the horses’ mouths, that they may obey us; and we turn about their whole body."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.4","order":"03.22.003.25002"},["b","4"],"Behold also the ships, which though",["i","they be"],"so great, and",["i","are"],"driven of fierce winds, yet are they turned about with a very small helm, whithersoever the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"governor"],"listeth."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.5","order":"03.22.003.25003"},["b","5"],"Even so the tongue is a little member, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"boasteth"],"great things. Behold, how great a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"matter"],"a little fire kindleth!"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.6","order":"03.22.003.25004"},["b","6"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"tongue"],["i","is"],"a fire, a world of iniquity: so is the tongue among our members, that it defileth the whole body, and setteth on fire the course of nature; and it is set on fire of hell."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.7","order":"03.22.003.25005"},["b","7"],"For every kind of beasts, and of birds, and of serpents, and of things in the sea, is tamed, and hath been tamed of mankind:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.8","order":"03.22.003.25006"},["b","8"],"But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"tongue"],"can no man tame;",["i","it is"],"an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"unruly"],"evil, full of deadly poison."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.9","order":"03.22.003.25007"},["b","9"],"Therewith bless we God, even the Father; and therewith",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"curse"],"we men, which are made after the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"similitude"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.10","order":"03.22.003.25008"},["b","10"],"Out of the same",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"mouth"],"proceedeth blessing and cursing. My brethren, these things ought not so to be."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.11","order":"03.22.003.25009"},["b","11"],"Doth a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"fountain"],"send forth at the same place sweet",["i","water"],"and bitter?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.12","order":"03.22.003.25010"},["b","12"],"Can the fig tree, my brethren, bear olive berries? either a vine, figs? so",["i","can"],"no fountain both yield salt water and fresh."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.13","order":"03.22.003.25011"},["b","13"],"Who",["i","is"],"a wise man and endued with knowledge among you? let him shew out of a good",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"conversation"],"his works with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"meekness"],"of wisdom."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.14","order":"03.22.003.25012"},["b","14"],"But if ye have bitter envying and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"strife"],"in your hearts,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"glory not"],", and lie not against the truth."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.15","order":"03.22.003.25013"},["b","15"],"This wisdom descendeth not from above, but",["i","is"],"earthly, sensual, devilish."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.16","order":"03.22.003.25014"},["b","16"],"For where",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"envying"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"strife"],["i","is,"],"there",["i","is"],"confusion and every evil work."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.17","order":"03.22.003.25015"},["b","17"],"But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"wisdom"],"that is from above is first pure, then peaceable, gentle,",["i","and"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"easy to be entreated"],", full of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"mercy"],"and good fruits, without partiality, and without",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.18","order":"03.22.003.25016"},["b","18"],"And the fruit of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"righteousness"],"is sown in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"peace"],"of them that make",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"peace"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.1a","order":"03.22.003.25017"},["b","1a"],["span.small","JST"],"James 3:1 …",["i","strive not for the mastery,"],"knowing that",["i","in so doing"],"we shall receive the greater condemnation."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.1b","order":"03.22.003.25019"},["b","1b"],["span.small","GR"],"(also) teachers."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.1c","order":"03.22.003.25021"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/82.3"},"D&C 82:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.2a","order":"03.22.003.25023"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"stumble, err."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.2b","order":"03.22.003.25025"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/offense"},"TG Offense"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.2c","order":"03.22.003.25027"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.1"},"Ps. 39:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/21.23"},"Prov. 21:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.2d","order":"03.22.003.25029"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perfection"},"TG Perfection"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.4a","order":"03.22.003.25031"},["b","4a"],["span.small","GR"],"helmsman, pilot."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.5a","order":"03.22.003.25033"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/boast"},"TG Boast"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rashness"},"Rashness"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.5b","order":"03.22.003.25035"},["b","5b"],["span.small","GR"],"forest."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.6a","order":"03.22.003.25037"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/16.27"},"Prov. 16:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/7.20.19-23"},"Mark 7:20 (19–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.14"},"Alma 12:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.121"},"D&C 88:121"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.8a","order":"03.22.003.25039"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gossip"},"TG Gossip"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/profanity"},"Profanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.8b","order":"03.22.003.25041"},["b","8b"],["span.small","GR"],"untameable, uncontrollable."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.9a","order":"03.22.003.25043"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.9b","order":"03.22.003.25045"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"},"TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.10a","order":"03.22.003.25047"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/12.34"},"Matt. 12:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/6.45"},"Luke 6:45"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.11a","order":"03.22.003.25049"},["b","11a"],["span.small","GR"],"spring, well.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.11.6-11"},"Moro. 7:11 (6–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.13a","order":"03.22.003.25051"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/12.13.13-19"},"Prov. 12:13 (13–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.13b","order":"03.22.003.25053"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meek"},"TG Meek"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.14a","order":"03.22.003.25055"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"TG Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.14b","order":"03.22.003.25057"},["b","14b"],["span.small","GR"],"do not assume superiority over."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.16a","order":"03.22.003.25059"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/envy"},"TG Envy"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.16b","order":"03.22.003.25061"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/contention"},"TG Contention"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.17a","order":"03.22.003.25063"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-intelligence-of"},"TG God, Intelligence of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wisdom"},"Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.17b","order":"03.22.003.25065"},["b","17b"],["span.small","GR"],"pliant, easily persuaded."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.17c","order":"03.22.003.25067"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-mercy-of"},"TG God, Mercy of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.17d","order":"03.22.003.25069"},["b","17d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.42"},"D&C 121:42"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.18a","order":"03.22.003.25071"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.18b","order":"03.22.003.25073"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"TG Peace"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.18c","order":"03.22.003.25075"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peacemakers"},"TG Peacemakers"],"."]]}
